    <div class="documentTop">      
      
      <h1>Departments</h1> 
      <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
       <div class="pageDescription"><p>The Office of the Prime Minister has thre departments. Each of the three departments is managed by a director general. The Office also has a Press- and Information section.&nbsp;</p> </div>       
    </div>
    
               
        
    
    <div id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_divPageContent" class="documentBody">
    
       
    
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/smk/The-Office-of-the-Prime-Minister/Organisation/Departments/The-Department-of-Administrative-Affairs.html?id=1605" title="">
                    The Department of Administrative Affairs
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The Department of Administrative Affairs assists the Secretary General in the preparation and follow-up of Council of State business. Constitutional issues are also addressed by this department.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/smk/The-Office-of-the-Prime-Minister/Organisation/Departments/The-Department-of-Domestic-Affairs.html?id=1608" title="">
                    The Department of Domestic Affairs
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The Department of Domestic Affairs assists the prime minister and the political staff with the ongoing coordination of the government's work. 
            </p>
            
        </div>
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/smk/The-Office-of-the-Prime-Minister/Organisation/Departments/the-department-of-international-affairs.html?id=1610" title="">
                    The Department of International Affairs
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The Department of International Affairs is responsible for advising on and processing all matters of an international nature.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    
        <div class="BoxDepartments expDiv">
            
            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/smk/The-Office-of-the-Prime-Minister/Organisation/Departments/press-and-information-section.html?id=1704" title="">
                    Communication  Section
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                Information activities in the Office of the Prime Minister are primarily the responsibility of the State Secretary for Press and Information Affairs.  
            </p>
            
        </div>
    
 
   
    </div>              
       
